        <title type="html"><![CDATA[网站快速支持自动切换暗黑模式和日常模式]]></title>
        <id>https://maxbee.github.io/post/hello-word</id>
        <link href="https://maxbee.github.io/post/hello-word">
        </link>
        <updated>2019-11-20T03:00:59.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>只需要在CSS添加以下代码即可：</p>
<pre><code>@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  body {
    background-color: #444;
    color: #e4e4e4;
  }
  a {
    color: #e39777;
  }
  img {
    filter: grayscale(30%);
  }
}
</code></pre>
<p>支持Firefox, Safari, Chrome浏览器</p>
<p><a href="%5Bhttps://tombrow.com/dark-mode-website-css%5D(https://tombrow.com/dark-mode-website-css)">参考来源</a></p>
]]></content>
